verbose_text: In healthy volunteers [XREF_BIBR] and in patients with type 2 diabetes [XREF_BIBR], 2 weeks of low-CHO diet (40% CHO, 45% fat, and 15% protein) resulted in lower TG level throughout 8-12-hour period in response to breakfast and lunch than after 2 weeks of low-fat diet (60% CHO, 25% fat, and 15% protein).
